        "content": "<p>I came across the instance <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/master/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L70\">https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/master/src/Init/Data/Option/Basic.lean#L70</a>, which isn't working:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">instance</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">DecidableRel</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"bp\">.</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Option</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">Option</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">inferInstance</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- fails</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I talked to <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"306601\">@Kyle Miller</span> about it, and he wrote this additional definition, which can derive the appropriate instance:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">instance</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">t</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">LT</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">s</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">DecidableRel</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">LT.lt</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">))]</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">DecidableRel</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">LT.lt</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">Option</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">LT.lt</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">inferInstance</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 260355216,
        "sender_full_name": "Scott Kovach",
        "timestamp": 1636074160
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Another example is that without this additional instance the following fails to find a <code>Decidable</code> instance.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Bool</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">some</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">none</span> <span class=\"k\">then</span> <span class=\"n\">true</span> <span class=\"k\">else</span> <span class=\"n\">false</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
